## 🛠️ Stack tecnológico

| Tecnología  | Uso                 |
| ----------- | ------------------- |
| Next.js     | Fullstack framework |
| React       | Interfaz            |
| TypeScript  | Tipado              |
| SQLite      | Base de datos       |
| TailwindCSS | Estilos             |
| SWR         | Manejo de datos     |
| bcryptjs    | Seguridad           |

---

## ⚡ Instalación

```bash
git clone https://github.com/santiago072004/supermarket-management-system.git
cd supermercado-dashboard
npm install
npm run dev
```

